The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | International | BlackBerrys a hit with teens
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             BlackBerrys a hit with teens
                            
	London, Sept. 13: The BlackBerry, once the preserve of macho investment bankers, is becoming one of the most sought after Christmas presents among teenagers this year.         
	Tech-savvy youngsters, who are obsessed with keeping in touch with their friends 24-hours-a-day, are particularly keen to make the most of the devices instant messaging service. The free service is widely seen as superior to an email or a text because it allows users to have a conversation with groups of friends in real time.                             THE DAILY TELEGRAPH                                                                                                                                                                   
